        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GBE for his great work on the placenta [<hi rend="italic">Nuove ricerche sulla placenta nei pesci cartilaginosi e ne mammiferi</hi> (1880)]. The relationship between placental structure and mammalian classification has always seemed interesting to CD.</p> 
